#logging.basicConfig(format='%(asctime)s : %(levelname)s : %(message)s', level=logging.INFO)
stoplist = set()
dictionary=corpora.Dictionary(line.lower().split() for line in open('newsdata_nobrand.txt'))
stop_ids=[
    dictionary.token2id[stopword]
    for stopword in stoplist
    if stopword in dictionary.token2id]

once_ids=[tokenid for tokenid, docfreq in iteritems(dictionary.dfs) if docfreq ==1]
dictionary.filter_tokens(stop_ids+once_ids)

In [12]:
topictime = []
for i in range(len(LEN)):
    b = []
    if i == 0:
        a = 0
    else:
        a = sum(LEN[k] for k in range(i))  
    for j in range(LEN[i]):
        doc = ldaseq.doc_topics(a+j)
        rank = np.argsort(doc)
        b.extend(rank[-1:])
    topictime.append(b)
In [13]:
topicdis = [[0 for i in range(num_topics)] for j in range(len(topictime))]
for i in range(len(topictime)):
    c = collections.Counter(topictime[i])
    c = dict(c)
    for j in range(len(c)):
        topicdis[i][j] = c[j]/LEN[i]
